1
00:00:00,083 --> 00:00:04,250
Interviewer: In this prison, were there visits from families and relatives?

2
00:00:04,833 --> 00:00:05,833
No, no

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:07,083
Interviewer: Didn’t anyone visit you?

4
00:00:07,541 --> 00:00:11,000
No one visited me, and even if someone came to ask about me here, they would tell him I’m not here

5
00:00:12,083 --> 00:00:13,083
Interviewer: Anyone else?

6
00:00:13,125 --> 00:00:16,583
As for me, my father came and asked about me, and they told him I wasn’t here

7
00:00:17,333 --> 00:00:20,000
Even though I was detained with them, they said, He’s not with us

8
00:00:21,458 --> 00:00:23,041
Interviewer: There were no visits? Witness: No

9
00:00:23,375 --> 00:00:27,708
They send him to the Faisaliya Center and tell him, Ask about him there, he went and asked

10
00:00:28,083 --> 00:00:30,208
Interviewer: Were there any special visits for other people?

11
00:00:30,416 --> 00:00:33,625
I don’t know—as for me, my family came and asked about me, and they told them–Not here
